'''Turin''' neɣ '''Aberfiw''' d [[agman]] agejdan deg [[Anagraw amesgunef|unagraw amesgunef]] n wemdan d waṭas n [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]] niden gar-asen ula kra n telmas n [[aslem|iselman]] d kra n [[aɣbalu|iɣlalen]]. Ɣer [[timsuṭad|temsuṭaṭ]] d wamur ameqran n n [[Timtegzitin|temtegzatin]], turin d tid yemmersen zdat n [[ajgu n uzagur|wejgu n uzagur]] deg yal iri n [[ul|wul]]. Tawuri n turin tga d tuṭṭfa n [[Uksijin|weksujin]] seg wezwu d usekcem-is s agensu n tregwa n yidammen yellan deg turin yakk d usufeɣ [[anaksid n ukaṛbun|CO2]] seg tregwa n yidammen ar wezwu deg yiwet n temhalt yettusemman [[asenfel n igazen]]. Tamhelt n [[Asgunf|usgunef]] tettili-d sɣuṛ n wallalen d inagrawen imaẓwalen yemgaraden ɣer tilmas yemgaraden (n [[Amuddir|imuddiren]]). Anda [[timsuṭad|temsuṭaṭ]] d [[agṭiṭ|yigṭaṭ]] d [[timraradin|temraradin]] ssemrasen-tt (ssexdamen-tt) [[tamaẓwalt|timaẓwalin-nsent]] yemgaraden i wsalel d usedhel n usgunef. Ma yella ɣer [[Tikuẓdarin|tkuẓdarin]] timenza, azwu yettwaseddu ar turin s tmaẓwalin [[tankart|timankarin]] (n uḥerjuḍ) iy tekken seg tsuffayin timawin i gan d allal mazal ixeddem ar [[Tikelmanin|tkelmanin]]. Tamaẓwalt n usgunef tagejdant ɣer wemdan yesseddawen tamhalt n usgunef tga d [[ilmendis]] 

Turin daɣen ssalelent tazizla (awezzeɛ) n wezwu id igellun s tesmamayt n [[iziker imsiwel|izukar imsiwlen]] ayen yettaǧǧan amdan yezmer ad yemmeslay.
<br>
Amdan ila (yesεa) sin n iberfiwen (turin). Yiwet d tamayeffust ma d tis snat d tazelmaṭ. Isnat zgant-d s agensu n [[amruj ademraw|imerjan idemrawen]]. Dɣa d aberfiw ayeffus i yugaren aberfiw azelmaṭ acku aberfiw azelmaṭ yebṭa tajumma-ynes yakk d wul. Turin d isnat ktent (uznent) 1,3 Kg. 

